  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1029">
<l>iṭumpaikkē koḷkalaṅ kollō kuṭumpattaik</l>
<l>kuṟṟa maṟaippā ṉuṭampu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it only to suffering that his body is exposed who undertakes to preserve his family from evil ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
